Spring Boot Dependencies to Add:
 1. Spring Web
For creating REST APIs.

Enables @RestController, @GetMapping, etc.

 Maven: spring-boot-starter-web

 2. Spring Data JPA
For database access using JPA (ORM).

Makes it easy to perform CRUD operations.

 Maven: spring-boot-starter-data-jpa

 3. MySQL Driver
To connect to your MySQL database.

 Maven: mysql-connector-j

 4. Spring Boot DevTools (Optional but helpful for dev)
Auto-restart the server on code changes.

Improves development experience.

 Maven: spring-boot-devtools

5. Spring Boot Validation (For input validation)
To use annotations like @NotNull, @Size, etc.

 Maven: spring-boot-starter-validation

 6. Spring Security (Optional now, but needed if you want login/authentication later)
Use later when adding user roles, login, JWT, etc.

 Maven: spring-boot-starter-security

7.lombok
